<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3689537>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Epipompilus mirabundus sp. nov., holotype, male. A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Habitus, lateral view. C. Head, frontal view. D. Cocoon. Scale bar: 1mm for A, B and D; 0.1 mm for C." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3689537/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3689539>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Male genitalia of Epipompilus mirabundus sp. nov., holotype. A. Genitalia, ventral view. B. Subgenital plate, ventral view. Scale bar: 0.1 mm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3689539/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3689545>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Epipompilus taree sp. nov., holotype, male. A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Head, frontal view. C. Genitalia, ventral view. D. Subgenital plate, ventral view. Scale bar: 1 mm for A; 0.1 mm for B, C and D." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3689545/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3689541>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Cocoon of Epipompilus mirabundus sp. nov., arrow pointed at the cocoon of E. mirabundus found sharing the mud nest of Sceliphron formosum, both cocoons emerged in the laboratory." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3689541/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3689543>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Epipompilus namadgi sp. nov., holotype, male. A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Head, frontal view. C. Genitalia, ventral view. D. Subgenital plate, ventral view. Scale bar: 1 mm for A; 0.1 mm for B, C and D." ;
